export default {
    'login.login': 'Login',
    'login.email': 'Email',
    'login.password': 'Password',
    'login.register': 'Register',
    'login.loginMethod': 'Other login methods',
    'login.validEmail': 'The input is not valid E-mail!',
    'login.requiredEmail': 'Please input your Email!',
    'login.requiredPassword': 'Please input your Password!',
    'login.lengPassword': 'Password at least 6 characters',
}
